Node.js runs on V8 engine which is developed by google and written in C++.Allows javaScript to run on your computer without which you could only run javaScript on browser.This is directly converted to machine code.
Node.js could 
->read & write files on a computer
->Connect to a database
->Act as a server for content

Why use Node
-> No need to learn extra language for server
-> Can share code between front aand back end
-> Huge amount of third party package & tools
-> Massive Community behind to help

Deprecated - features thatmay not be available in the future and this is marked with a line crossing the word.
